owner
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

The owner command is run whenever an e-mail message is sent to the
LISTNAME-owner or LISTNAME-moderator address for a mailing list.  Access
to these two addresses can be restricted with the block_headers
configuration setting.

See Also:
   help admin_moderate
   help configset_aliases
   help configset_block_headers
   help configset_moderators
   help configset_owners

